Make it even more treats for you.

00:04:05.510 --> 00:04:07.510
There's nothing wrong with your TV.

00:04:07.510 --> 00:04:09.510
I'm in black and white for a reason.

00:04:09.510 --> 00:04:11.510
I'm demonstrating how you can take something old,

00:04:11.510 --> 00:04:12.510
like a black and white movie,

00:04:12.510 --> 00:04:14.510
