00:06:40.330 --> 00:06:43.330
Damn, why would pancakes be stuck to the ceiling in the first place?

00:06:43.330 --> 00:06:45.330
I don't know. I just thought it'd be fun.

00:06:46.330 --> 00:06:48.330
Well, maybe we should try to improve something

00:06:48.330 --> 00:06:50.330
that actually has something to do with the real world.

00:06:50.330 --> 00:06:53.330
