00:07:10.330 --> 00:07:12.330
New and improved toilet paper?

00:07:12.330 --> 00:07:14.330
Not great, but better.

00:07:15.330 --> 00:07:16.330
I've got an idea.

00:07:16.330 --> 00:07:19.330
What's the most annoying, obnoxious, irritating thing

00:07:19.330 --> 00:07:21.330
