00:07:29.330 --> 00:07:31.330
Tom and Stuffer High

00:07:31.330 --> 00:07:33.330
Tom and Stuffer High

00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:36.330
Howl at halls of Tom and Stuffer High

00:07:36.330 --> 00:07:40.330
Honored excellence forever at Tom and Stuffer High

00:07:40.330 --> 00:07:41.330
