00:07:52.330 --> 00:07:55.330
Who says you can't teach an old song new tricks?

00:07:55.330 --> 00:07:56.330
So let's improve the anthem.

00:07:56.330 --> 00:07:57.330
Great. We can work on it now.

00:07:57.330 --> 00:07:58.330
Okay.

