01:49:06.110 --> 01:49:07.110
It's all about.

01:49:07.110 --> 01:49:09.110
Orange and purple and green.

01:49:09.110 --> 01:49:10.110
Color.

01:49:11.110 --> 01:49:13.110
Now, the sneaking begins again.

01:49:13.110 --> 01:49:15.110
With Are You Afraid of the Dark?

01:49:15.110 --> 01:49:33.400
She already left.

01:49:33.400 --> 01:49:35.400
But her car's still outside.

01:49:35.400 --> 01:49:37.400
It's absolutely forever.

01:49:38.400 --> 01:49:39.400
Ever.

01:49:40.400 --> 01:49:43.580
Andrew.

01:49:43.580 --> 01:49:51.710
Louise.

01:49:51.710 --> 01:49:53.710
Louise, is that you?

01:49:53.710 --> 01:49:54.710
Over here.

01:49:54.710 --> 01:49:57.920
Living room.

01:49:57.920 --> 01:50:10.310
Louise?

01:50:11.310 --> 01:50:12.310
I'm upstairs.

01:50:13.310 --> 01:50:15.310
Please, come help me.

01:50:15.310 --> 01:50:16.310
Please.

01:50:16.310 --> 01:50:18.310
How'd you get there?

01:50:21.310 --> 01:50:27.780
He's from a tavern.

01:50:27.780 --> 01:50:28.780
He must be Master Raymond.

01:50:28.780 --> 01:50:29.780
Who cares?

01:50:29.780 --> 01:50:30.780
He was a creep, remember?

01:50:30.780 --> 01:50:32.780
Now he's a ghost creep.

01:50:32.780 --> 01:50:34.780
We have to find Louise.

01:50:34.780 --> 01:50:35.780
How about you find her?

01:50:35.780 --> 01:50:36.780
I stay here.

01:50:36.780 --> 01:50:37.780
No.

01:50:37.780 --> 01:50:38.780
I need you.

01:50:39.780 --> 01:50:40.780
You do?

01:50:40.780 --> 01:50:41.780
Yeah.

01:50:42.780 --> 01:50:43.780
You're smart.

01:50:44.780 --> 01:50:46.780
You think of the things that I don't.

01:50:46.780 --> 01:50:49.320
Yeah, yeah.

01:50:49.320 --> 01:50:51.320
I do, don't I?

01:50:51.320 --> 01:50:52.320
Come on.

01:50:52.320 --> 01:50:53.320
You have to look upstairs.

01:50:53.320 --> 01:51:51.350
Just a little schmunkin' head.

01:51:51.350 --> 01:51:52.350
Come in.

01:51:52.350 --> 01:51:54.350
It really is you.

01:51:54.350 --> 01:51:55.350
What happened?

01:51:56.350 --> 01:51:57.350
Don't worry.

01:51:57.350 --> 01:51:58.350
I'm okay.

01:51:58.350 --> 01:52:00.350
I found this little baby,

01:52:00.350 --> 01:52:02.350
and we can go just as soon as he's asleep.

01:52:03.350 --> 01:52:05.350
I thought for sure that you were hurt.

01:52:05.350 --> 01:52:06.350
Or even...

01:52:06.350 --> 01:52:07.350
No.

01:52:07.350 --> 01:52:08.350
I'm fine.

01:52:09.350 --> 01:52:11.350
I've never been better.

01:52:12.350 --> 01:52:17.960
Here.

01:52:17.960 --> 01:52:18.960
This is for you.

01:52:18.960 --> 01:52:44.280
So sad.

01:52:44.280 --> 01:53:04.780
Help me, Louise.

01:53:04.780 --> 01:53:06.780
It's me.

01:53:06.780 --> 01:53:08.780
It's really me.

01:53:08.780 --> 01:53:09.780
I'm trapped.

01:53:09.780 --> 01:54:57.420
You're such a small boy.

01:54:57.420 --> 01:54:58.420
Not small.

01:54:58.420 --> 01:54:59.420
I'm not scared of you.

01:54:59.420 --> 01:55:01.420
No matter.

01:55:01.420 --> 01:55:03.420
When the sun sets,

01:55:03.420 --> 01:55:05.420
her soul

01:55:05.420 --> 01:55:10.400
will be mine.

01:55:10.400 --> 01:55:11.400
Who are you?

01:55:11.400 --> 01:55:12.400
What do you want?

01:55:12.400 --> 01:55:15.400
Her energy will keep me alive.

01:55:15.400 --> 01:55:18.400
Keep this house alive.

01:55:18.400 --> 01:55:23.400
And she'll be part of us forever.

01:55:24.400 --> 01:55:26.400
You're a monster.

01:55:26.400 --> 01:55:30.780
Choose my words carefully if I were you.

01:55:31.780 --> 01:55:35.780
Or you might be next.

01:55:35.780 --> 01:55:37.780
Don't touch that!

01:55:37.780 --> 01:56:12.260
There's no use in running.

01:56:12.260 --> 01:56:16.260
The sun is almost down.

01:56:16.260 --> 01:56:20.260
She is mine.

01:56:20.260 --> 01:56:25.560
Don't kill anybody.

01:56:25.560 --> 01:56:28.560
Silly boy with silly toys.

01:56:28.560 --> 01:56:38.470
You won't fool me again.

01:56:38.470 --> 01:56:45.270
Dear, you too.

01:56:45.270 --> 01:56:54.980
Little one.

01:56:54.980 --> 01:56:56.980
Little boy.

01:56:56.980 --> 01:56:58.980
They're mine now.

01:57:01.980 --> 01:57:07.980
No!

01:57:07.980 --> 01:57:08.980
Violet.

01:57:08.980 --> 01:57:10.980
What are you doing?

01:57:10.980 --> 01:57:12.980
I won't let you do this.

01:57:12.980 --> 01:57:14.980
You dare.

01:57:14.980 --> 01:57:16.980
Go against my wish.

01:57:16.980 --> 01:57:18.980
They're so young.

01:57:18.980 --> 01:57:20.980
This is not your concern.

01:57:20.980 --> 01:57:25.290
Return to the walls.

01:57:25.290 --> 01:57:28.290
She's so like my poor little Jane.

01:57:28.290 --> 01:57:30.290
But no, no.

01:57:30.290 --> 01:57:37.500
What happened?

01:57:37.500 --> 01:57:40.940
Thank you.

01:57:40.940 --> 01:57:50.420
Still open and split, boys.

01:57:50.420 --> 01:57:52.800
Yes!

01:57:52.800 --> 01:58:32.820
Still stands.

01:58:32.820 --> 01:58:33.820
And to this day,

01:58:33.820 --> 01:58:35.820
people still disappear

01:58:35.820 --> 01:58:37.820
when the moon is full

01:58:37.820 --> 01:58:39.820
on February 29.

01:58:39.820 --> 01:58:52.760
Time to go.

01:58:52.760 --> 01:58:54.760
You go first.

01:58:54.760 --> 01:58:57.760
No after you.

01:58:57.760 --> 01:58:58.760
Not me.

01:58:58.760 --> 01:59:00.760
You go, Frank.

01:59:00.760 --> 01:59:02.760
I'll go after Gary goes.

01:59:02.760 --> 01:59:04.760
I'm not going first.

01:59:04.760 --> 02:00:29.000
My ultimate ESPN Sports Center highlight

02:00:29.000 --> 02:00:30.000
goes like this.

02:00:30.000 --> 02:00:32.000
Loose ball in the end zone.

02:00:32.000 --> 02:00:34.000
Fall on it, no chance.

02:00:34.000 --> 02:00:35.000
My feet are light,

02:00:35.000 --> 02:00:37.000
and I've got the moves.

02:00:37.000 --> 02:00:39.000
At the 50, I see Myers.

02:00:39.000 --> 02:00:40.000
Not now, Chris.

02:00:40.000 --> 02:00:42.000
I'm a busy man.

02:00:42.000 --> 02:00:45.000
And as I cross the goal line, I laugh.

02:00:45.000 --> 02:00:47.000
Knowing my agent has just cut a deal

02:00:47.000 --> 02:00:49.000
for my very own fitness video.

02:00:49.000 --> 02:00:51.000
Yeah, that's my sport, sir.

